high_descs: Turn around, go around the left side of the table, then move around the table and turn right to face the table.
Pick up the egg on the table.
Bring the egg to the microwave on the left, above the stove.
Heat the egg in the microwave.
Take the heated egg to the trash can at the right of the stove.
Put the heated egg in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated egg in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn around and walk around the center table to face the opposite side.
Pick up the egg on the center table.
Turn left and step forward to face the microwave.
Heat the egg in the microwave and remove it.
Step to the right to face the trash can.
Place the egg in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To heat an egg and place it in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn right, turn right at the wall, turn right at the fridge, turn right again to face the kitchen island.
Pick up the egg in front of the gold plate.
Turn and walk to the stove and look up at the microwave.
Open the microwave door, put the egg in the microwave to the left of the apple, close the door, heat the egg, open the door, pick up the egg, and close the door.
Walk over to face the silver bin to the right of the stove.
Put the egg inside of the bin.
anns.task_desc: To heat an egg and put it inside the silver bin.
